          <section class="box" data-cmsid="94409"> 
           <h2>Types of Publications</h2> 
           <dl class="index-list h3-headings pub-types-list"> 
            <dt> 
             <a href="/health/publications/booklets.shtml">Booklets</a> 
            </dt> 
            <dd> 
             <span><a href="/health/publications/booklets.shtml" class="to-start"> <span> <img src="/images/health-and-outreach/nimh-schizophrenia-publication-cover-thumbnail_103158_1.png" alt="Schizophrenia" data-cmsid="103158"></span> </a></span>Detailed publications about the signs, symptoms, treatment, and current research on specific mental illnesses and related topics. 
            </dd> 
            <dt> 
             <a href="/health/publications/easy-to-read.shtml">Brochures (Easy-to-Read)</a> 
            </dt> 
            <dd> 
             <span><a href="/health/publications/easy-to-read.shtml" class="to-start"> <span> <img src="/images/pubs/covers-thumbnails/sp-thumbnail-cover-adhd-ez-trifold_96363_6.png" alt="Cubierta del folleto Trastorno de Déficit de Atención e Hiperactividad (Fácil de Leer)" data-cmsid="96363"></span> </a></span>Short publications with basic information about signs, symptoms, and related treatment of specific mental illnesses. 
            </dd> 
            <dt> 
             <a href="/health/publications/fact-sheets.shtml">Fact Sheets</a> 
            </dt> 
            <dd> 
             <span><a href="/health/publications/fact-sheets.shtml" class="to-start"> <span> <img src="/images/pubs/covers-thumbnails/neuroimaging-faq_cvr_103331_4.png" alt="Neuroimaging FAQ" data-cmsid="103331"></span> </a></span>Brief overviews and frequently asked questions about specific mental health topics. 
            </dd> 
           </dl> 
          </section> 
